{"surah": 94, "verses": [{"id": 1, "text": "أَلَمْ نَشْرَحْ لَكَ صَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>رَكَ <span class=end>١</span>"}, {"id": 2, "text": "وَوَضَعْنَا عَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نك</tajweed>َ وِزْرَكَ <span class=end>٢</span>"}, {"id": 3, "text": "ٱلَّذ<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>ِىٓ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نق</tajweed>َضَ ظَهْرَكَ <span class=end>٣</span>"}, {"id": 4, "text": "وَرَفَعْنَا لَكَ ذِكْرَكَ <span class=end>٤</span>"}, {"id": 5, "text": "فَإِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ مَعَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا <span class=end>٥</span>"}, {"id": 6, "text": "إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ مَعَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا <span class=end>٦</span>"}, {"id": 7, "text": "فَإِذَا فَرَغْتَ فَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=ikhafa>نص</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed> <span class=end>٧</span>"}, {"id": 8, "text": "وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>رْغَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed> <span class=end>٨</span>"}]}